            "title": "NezveRerai Umntwana",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2025-12-10T11:32:56+00:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EWed, 12/10/2025 - 11:32\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-04-28T06:16:12+00:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 04/28/2026 - 06:16\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "body": "\u003Cp\u003ERerai Umntwana chirongwa chekurera vana chakagadzirirwa vabereki, vanochengeta vana, uye vanopa maservice muZimbabwe. Chirongwa cheBazi reHutano neKuchengetwa kweVana, nerutsigiro kubva kuUNICEF Zimbabwe nekuHurumende yeJapan.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENezveApplication yeRerai Umntwana\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERerai Umntwana yakagadzirwa kuti ipindure zvinodiwa nezvinofarirwa nevabereki nevanovachengeta vana muZimbabwe. Vabereki vazhinji vanosangana nematambudziko ekusawana ruzivo rwakanaka rwakavimbika pamusoro pekudya kunovaka muviri kwevana, hutano nekukura kwavo. Chirongwa ichi chinovavarira kuzadzikisa matambudziko aya nekupa vabereki nevanovachengeta vana vadiki mazano anoshanda, anoenderana netsika, uye zvingashandisika pane zvekudya zvinovaka muviri, hutano hwevana, kukura nekurera vana.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EZvakabatana nemitemo yehutano yemunyika nezvirongwa zvekushandirapamwe, Rerai Umntwana yakagadzirirwa kubatanidza uye kuve nyore kuwana. Pamusoro pezvo, chine mifananidzo nezvinyorwa zviri nyore kushandisa pafoni pamusoro peunyanzvi hwekuva mubereki.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERerai Umntwana chirongwa chinotsigira kurerwa kwevana zvakanaka uye zvine hanya. Chinangwa chayo ndechekupa ruzivo rwakakwana nezvekukura kwevana vachiri vadiki nekuchengetwa kwavo nevabereki nenzira inogamuchirika kuvabereki. Rerai Umntwana inobatsira kuparadzira mashoko neruzivo zvine chekuita nezvirwere, kudzivirira zvirwere uye kuchengetedzwa kwevana.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Carticle class=\"align-center media media--type-image media--view-mode-default\"\u003E          \u003Cdiv data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/21771/field_media_image/en/default\" class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\"\u003E                  \u003Cdiv class=\"field__item\"\u003E  \u003Cimg src=\"/sites/zimbabwe/files/styles/content_1200xh_/public/2026-04/rerai-umntwana-logo-final_1.png?itok=lZuA4MRL\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" alt=\"Rerai Umntwana Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" class=\"image-style-content-1200xh-\"\u003E\u003C/div\u003E          \u003C/div\u003E  \u003C/article\u003E\u003Cp\u003EApp iyi  inogona kushandiswa nemabazi anoshanda nevana nevabereki sechishandiso chekuwana ruzivo mubasa ravo nevabereki, uye sechishandiso chekuvaka hukama hunovimbika pamwe nekudyidzana kunobatsira vana vadiki.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EApp iyi yakagadzirwa kutsigira vabereki kuti vatore chikamu muzviitwa zvinokurudzira kukura nekusimudzira mwana kuburikidza nemitambo nezviitwa zvavanoita nevana vavo, uye inovabatsirawo kutevera kukura, nemamiriro ehutano hwemwana.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EApp iyi ine library rakapfuma rezvinyorwa nemavhidhiyo akaiswa mumapoka ezvinyorwa zvine misoro inotevera:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003EKutamba nekudzidza\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EKudya kunovaka muviri nekuyamwisa\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EKurera vana zvine hanya\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EKuchengeteka nekuzvichengetedza\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EHutano nekuchengetedzeka zvakanaka\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EKuchengetedzeka zvakanaka kwevabereki\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EApp iyi inoshandisa ruzivo rwezuva rekuzvarwa kwemwana, kuva mukomana kana musikana, pamwe neimwe information yakaita sehuremu hwemwana ichapinzwa nemubereki, ichabatsira kupa kurudziro nenhungamiro inoenderana nemwana.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EZvimwe zvirimo muapp iyi zvakawanikwa, zvakagadziridzwa uye zvakashandurwa nemvumo kubva kuRaising Children Network Australia (\u003Ca href=\"https://raisingchildren.net.au/\"\u003ERaising Children Network\u003C/a\u003E), Real Play Coalition (\u003Ca href=\"https://www.realplaycoalition.com\"\u003Ehttps://www.realplaycoalition.com\u003C/a\u003E), Afinidata (\u003Ca href=\"https://afinidata.com/en/home/\"\u003Ehttps://afinidata.com/en/home/\u003C/a\u003E).\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EApp iyi inoda internet kuti ikwanise kuita download zvirimo uye iratidze zvirimo.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E App iyi inogonawo kushanda isina internet munzvimbo dzine internet shoma. Chinodiwa ndechekuti pakutanga mushandisi amboenda painternet odownloader app opinda muapp. Mushandisi anogona kusarudza kuburikidza neApp Settings kudownloader zvirimo zvinoenderana nezera remwana wake parizvino, kana kudownloader zvirimo zvese kuitira kuti akwanise kushandisa App pasina internet zvachose. \u003C/p\u003E",
            "mandatory": 1,
