            "id": 36,
            "type": "Basic page",
            "title": "Ikhasi ngathi",
            "created_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2025-12-10T11:32:57+00:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003EWed, 12/10/2025 - 11:32\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "updated_at": "\u003Ctime datetime=\"2026-04-28T06:17:54+00:00\" class=\"datetime\"\u003ETue, 04/28/2026 - 06:17\u003C/time\u003E\n",
            "body": "\u003Cp\u003EI-Rerai Umntwana yi-app yokukhulisa abantwana eyenzelwe ababelethi, abatlhogomeli, nabahlinzeki beenkonzo e-Zimbabwe. Yi-app yomNyango wezamaPhilo nokuTjheja abantwana, esekelwa yi-UNICEF Zimbabwe ngemali evela kuRhulumende we-Japan.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EMayelana nesicelo\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI-Rerai Umntwana yasungulwa ukuphendula iindingo ezihlukileko neenrhuluphelo zababelethi nabatlhogomeli e-Zimbabwe. Ababelethi abanengi baqalene neentjhijilo zokufinyelela okulinganiselweko kwelwazi elithembekileko, elisekelwe ebufakazini malungana nokudla kwabantwana, ipilo nokuthuthuka. I-app le ihlose ukuvala isikhala ngokunikela ababelethi nabatlhogomeli babantwana abancani iseluleko esisebenzako, esihlobene namasiko, namathulusi wezondleko, ipilo, ukuthuthukiswa kwabantwana nokukhulisa abantwana.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENgokukhambisana nemigomo yezamaphilo kazwelonke kanye neenhlelo ezihlanganisiweko, i-Rerai Umntwana yenzelwe bona ifake woke umuntu begodu ifinyeleleke. Ukungezelela, inezinto ezibonakalako ezilula nezisebenziseka lula zokukhulisa abantwana.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EI-Rerai Umntwana yihlelo elisekela ukukhulisa abantwana okuphendulako, okuhle. Umnqopho wayo kukunikela ilwazi elipheleleko malungana nokukhula kwabantwana abasesebancani nokutlhogonyelwa kwababelethi ngendlela efanele ababelethi. U-Rerai Umntwana angasekela ukusabalaliswa kwemilayezo nelwazi eliphathelene nokugula nokukhandela nokuvikelwa kwabantwana.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Carticle class=\"align-center media media--type-image media--view-mode-default\"\u003E          \u003Cdiv data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/21776/field_media_image/en/default\" class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\"\u003E                  \u003Cdiv class=\"field__item\"\u003E  \u003Cimg src=\"/sites/zimbabwe/files/styles/content_1200xh_/public/2026-04/rerai-umntwana-logo-final_2.png?itok=FfLGjQDq\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" alt=\"Rerai Umntwana Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" class=\"image-style-content-1200xh-\"\u003E\u003C/div\u003E          \u003C/div\u003E  \u003C/article\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI-app le ingasetjenziswa babantu abanikela ngeenkonzo njengesisetjenziswa emsebenzini wabo nababelethi begodu njengethuluzi lokwakha ubudlelwano obuthembekileko nokusebenzisana ukuzuzisa abantwana abancani.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EI-app le yenzelwe ukusekela ababelethi bona bazibandakanye emisebenzini ekhuthazako ngokusebenzisa imidlalo nemisebenzi nabantwana babo begodu izobasiza ukutjheja ukukhula kwabantwana, ukuthuthuka nobujamo bepilo.\u003Cbr\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI-app inelayibhrari ecebileko yama-atikili namavidiyo ahlanganiswe ngaphasi kweenkoro ezithi:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003EDlala nokufunda\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkudla okunomsoco nokumunyisa\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkukhulisa abantwana abaphendulako\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkuphepha nokuvikeleka\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EIpilo nokuphila kuhle\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003EUkuphila kuhle kwababelethi\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI-app isebenzisa ilwazi ngelanga lokubelethwa komntwana, ubulili neminye imininingwana efakwe mzali ukuncoma okuqukethwe okufaneleko nesiqondiso esilungiselelwe.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOkunye okuqukethwe kilo loke i-app kutholwe, kwatjhugululwa begodu kwatjhugululwa ngemvumo evela ku-Raising Children Network Australia (\u003Ca href=\"https://raisingchildren.net.au/\"\u003ERaising Children Network\u003C/a\u003E), Real Play Coalition (\u003Ca href=\"https://www.realplaycoalition.com\"\u003Ehttps://www.realplaycoalition.com\u003C/a\u003E), Afinidata (\u003Ca href=\"https://afinidata.com/en/home/\"\u003Ehttps://afinidata.com/en/home\u003C/a\u003E/).\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI-app izokutlhoga ukuxhumana kwe-inthanethi ukudawuniloda okuqukethwe nokutjengisa okuqukethwe kwemidiya.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI-app le ingasebenza ngendlela engasebenziko eendaweni ezine-inthanethi elinganiselwe. Umbandela walokho kukuthi umsebenzisi bekasolo a-inthanethi okungenani kanye lokha nakadawuniloda i-app begodu angena kiyo. Umsebenzisi angakhetha ngokusebenzisa amaSethingi we-app ukudawuniloda okuqukethwe kohlelo lokusebenza okuqondene neminyaka yomntwanakhe yamanje nofana ukudawuniloda koke okumumethweko ukwenzela bona akwazi ukukusebenzisa ngendlela engaxhunyiwe ku-inthanethi.\u003C/p\u003E",
